                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
                    <a href="/projects"
                        class="bg-black hover:bg-gray-800 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition duration-300 shadow-md">
                        Lihat Karya Saya
                    </a>
                    <a href="/about"
                        class="bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 text-black border border-gray-300 font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition duration-300">
                        Kenali Lebih Jauh
                    </a>
